{"tid":840472,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"念念不忘必有回響？","createTime":"2018-09-28T19:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T13:47:32.000Z","uid":142508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"70702639d6246cfb292eb80edf6b1e2350d7e866","tid":840472,"uid":142508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T19:33:49.000Z","msg":"真定假呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e318e55d996c6a5dc6f02976cef2efc4046cdda4","tid":840472,"uid":144466,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T19:46:13.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀，去強姦。人生沒有那麼多時間給你演內心戲。愛她就去搞她，喜歡就去強姦。表白有什麼用還是會被拒絕。追不到就下藥，翻臉就殺了她。大不了就被殺，你連投胎都不敢還好意思說愛她。投胎長大之後找到她繼續強姦，強姦到讓她開始懷疑自己的人生，讓她覺得她人生的意義就是被你強姦。"},{"pid":"7f3d86e2517bbd165f93c6accc44c9df6bfca224","tid":840472,"uid":36402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T20:14:01.000Z","msg":"難忘的因你太念念才難忘"},{"pid":"d4d32d43c6a87388eadb8957ded39d81cf7bb86d","tid":840472,"uid":168135,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T22:30:42.000Z","msg":"世間所有的相遇，都是久別重逢"},{"pid":"a7cf1d84b256f02969343c5a57edf161ef92c914","tid":840472,"uid":205307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T23:00:29.000Z","msg":"冇用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係拎黎安慰自己"},{"pid":"b3a789a5e8476f416d1dc0723e6d43fd04112713","tid":840472,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T00:28:09.000Z","msg":"醒下啦"},{"pid":"3036e245964b971b442b09964372e8bc3c778c3c","tid":840472,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T00:28:41.000Z","msg":"假"},{"pid":"0a6dd78b7544e13c0d975495557c2f7777fa9bba","tid":840472,"uid":92042,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T00:40:36.000Z","msg":"得自己一個念念不忘有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0dd147ae9f63612a5ff2abdb62d0ed1d7320ff","tid":840472,"uid":142508,"like":0,"d